# Hardware Serup Instructions

### Parts List

1. Pref Board (DIMENSIONS)
2. Soldering Iron
3. Solder (Recommended: flux core 63-37)
4. 1&ohm; resistor
5. LED fire mimicing circuit strip
6. 100mH Inductor
7. Tactile push switch
8. Solar Panel (Recommended: open terminals 3v output minimum)
9. AA battery and holder (Recommended: 2750mAh Minimum: 850mAh)
10. 1N5819 Diode
11. 30 AWG Insulated Tinned Copper Wire
12. 24 AWG Insulated Tinned Copper Wire
13. Optional: 16 AWG 99.9% Pure Solid Copper Wire
14. IC805 or YX805 Package
15. Optional: Multimeter for testing
16. Access to a 3D printer

### Step-by-Step


### Wired Layout
Battery negative (-) $\rightarrow$ common gnd
Battery positive (+) $\rightarrow$ IC805 (YX805) vcc
Battery positive (+) $\rightarrow$ Inductor (100mH)
Inductor (100mH) $\rightarrow$ 1&ohm; resistor
1&ohm; resistor $\rightarrow$ LED (+) vcc
IC805 (YX805) $\rightarrow$ LED (+) vcc
IC805 (YX805) $\rightarrow$ common gnd
LED (-) gnd $\rightarrow$ common gnd
solar panel (+) vcc $\rightarrow$ anode 1N5819 diode
cathode 1N5819 $\rightarrow$ IC805 (YX805) sol
1 end of switch $\rightarrow$ IC805 (YX805) sol
1 end of switch $\rightarrow$ common gnd
solar panel (-) gnd $\rightarrow$ common gnd



